==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irrevoluble
<hw>Ir*rev"o*lu*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>That has no
finite period of revolution; not revolving.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The dateless and <qex>irrevoluble</qex> circle of eternity.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irrhetorical</ent>⟦br⟧
